      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Two-Pointer Approach\nDescription: Employ two pointers to traverse the sorted list \nof robots and resolve collisions by comparing\n healths in a single pass.\n",
